% ║   CRYPT OF THE FORGOTTEN KING — A Logic Dungeon Crawler             ║
% ║                                                                     ║
% ║   Play by asserting facts and asking queries!                       ║
% ║                                                                     ║
% ║   Start:   Hero has location entrance.                              ║
% ║            Hero has hp 20.                                          ║
% ║   Move:    Hero has location torch_hall.                            ║
% ║   Pickup:  Hero has holding torch.                                  ║
% ║   Query:   Is Hero alive?                                          ║
% ║            Who is dangerous?                                        ║
% ║            Is entrance connected_to torch_hall?                     ║
% ║            Who has holding something?  (inventory)                  ║
% ╚═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

