% ─── GAME RULES ════════════════════════════════════════════════════

% --- Danger assessment ---
X is dangerous if X has monster M.
X is trapped if X has trap T.
X is dark if X is a dark_room.
X is safe if X is a room and X is not dangerous and X is not trapped.

% --- Reachability ---
% "X is adjacent_to Y" means you can go from Y to X
X is adjacent_to Y if Y is connected_to X.

% Can the hero move to a room?
X is reachable_from Y if Y is connected_to X and Y is not locked_to X.

% --- What can be found ---
X is lootable if X has loot I.

% --- Monster classification ---
X is a minion if X has hp H and X is not a boss.

% --- Exploration ---
% A room is on the critical path if it connects to the throne room or exit
X is on critical_path if X is connected_to throne_room.
X is on critical_path if X is connected_to exit_gate.
X is on critical_path if X is connected_to hidden_passage.

% --- Item utility ---
X is offensive if X is a weapon.
X is offensive if X is a spell.
X is defensive if X is a shield.
X is usable if X is a consumable.

% --- Victory ---
% To win: reach exit_gate holding the crown
% (Player asserts: Hero has location exit_gate. Hero has holding crown.)
X is a victor if X has location exit_gate and X has holding crown.

% --- The gauntlet: rooms you must pass through to reach the crown ---
% crown is in treasure_vault
% treasure_vault requires iron_key (from prison)
% prison is past tortured_ghost
% throne_room is past forgotten_king (the boss)
% exit_gate requires passing through hidden_passage (traps!)

% ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
%  HOW TO PLAY (via the Axiom REPL)
% ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
%
%  1. SETUP — Assert your starting state:
%       Hero has location entrance.
%       Hero has hp 20.
%
%  2. LOOK AROUND — Query the world:
%       Is entrance dangerous?              % check for monsters
%       Is entrance trapped?                % check for traps
%       Is entrance dark?                   % need a torch?
%       Who is adjacent_to entrance?        % where can you go?
%       Who has loot torch?                 % where is the torch? (entrance)
%
%  3. PICK UP ITEMS — Assert you're holding them:
%       Hero has holding torch.
%
%  4. MOVE — Assert new location:
%       Hero has location torch_hall.
%
%  5. CHECK MONSTERS — Before entering:
%       Is guard_room dangerous?            % Yes! (skeleton_guard)
%       Who has monster skeleton_guard?      % which room
%
%  6. FIGHT — You manage combat by hp facts:
%       % Your rusty_sword does 4 damage to skeleton_guard (hp 6)
%       % skeleton_guard attacks you for 2 (minus shield defense)
%       % After 2 rounds: skeleton_guard is dead, you took ~4 damage
%
%  7. LOCKED DOORS:
%       Is throne_room locked_to treasure_vault?  % Yes
%       % Get the iron_key from prison first!
%       Hero has holding iron_key.
%
%  8. THE BOSS:
%       % forgotten_king in throne_room: 15 hp, 5 attack
%       % Use holy_water (10 dmg to undead!) + weapon
%       Is forgotten_king undead?           % Yes - holy water is effective!
%
%  9. VICTORY:
%       Hero has holding crown.
%       Hero has location exit_gate.
%       Is Hero a victor?                   % Did you win?
%
%  STRATEGY TIPS:
%  - Get the torch FIRST (entrance) — 3 rooms are dark
%  - Grab rusty_sword + leather_shield from armory early
%  - health_potions are in alchemy_lab and sewer
%  - iron_key in prison unlocks treasure_vault
%  - holy_water from shrine is devastating vs the undead boss
%  - The crown is in treasure_vault behind the boss
%  - Escape through: hidden_passage → exit_gate
%  - Watch for traps in pit_room, sewer, hidden_passage!
% ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
